740
00:51:26,309 --> 00:51:28,019
How is your father?

741
00:51:28,102 --> 00:51:32,398
I don't know, I haven't been able
to get in touch with him for a week,

742
00:51:32,481 --> 00:51:34,525
He's fine,

743
00:51:34,609 --> 00:51:40,656
Last time I talked to him, he was fine, He's
been fine for months now, Nine months,

744
00:51:40,740 --> 00:51:42,783
He was a great man,

745
00:51:42,867 --> 00:51:44,702
He still is,

746
00:51:48,164 --> 00:51:50,583
You're gonna fail me, aren't you?

747
00:51:50,666 --> 00:51:55,129
I'm giving you another chance
to redo the problem set,

748
00:51:55,212 --> 00:51:59,175
You need an A,
You're quite capable of earning one,

749
00:52:01,260 --> 00:52:03,596
Thank you,

750
00:52:06,682 --> 00:52:08,851
- Professor Bhandari?
- Yeah,

751
00:52:08,934 --> 00:52:11,103
Don't worry about me, OK?

752
00:52:11,186 --> 00:52:17,234
I'm gonna write you a really nice fat set
of answers that you're really gonna like,

753
00:52:51,268 --> 00:52:54,855
<i> Hi. We're not here.
