774
00:55:47,442 --> 00:55:50,404
- I know,
- Well, aren't you cold?

775
00:55:50,445 --> 00:55:53,907
Of course I am,
I'm freezing my ass off.

776
00:55:53,949 --> 00:55:56,326
So what are you doing out here?

777
00:55:56,410 --> 00:56:02,374
It's too hot in the house, The radiators
clank and I couldn't concentrate,

778
00:56:06,753 --> 00:56:09,881
I've been calling and calling,
Did you not get my messages?

779
00:56:09,923 --> 00:56:12,259
It's a distraction,

780
00:56:12,300 --> 00:56:15,595
I didn't know what was going on,
I had to drive all the way out here,

781
00:56:15,679 --> 00:56:18,139
I can see that,

782
00:56:18,223 --> 00:56:21,935
- Why don't you answer the phone?
- I'm sorry, Catherine,

783
00:56:22,018 --> 00:56:26,773
But it's a question of priorities,
and work takes priority, You know that,

784
00:56:26,856 --> 00:56:29,276
You're working?

785
00:56:29,317 --> 00:56:32,112
Goddamn it!

786
00:56:32,153 --> 00:56:34,489
I'm working!

787
00:56:37,200 --> 00:56:39,536
I mean, I say "I,"

788
00:56:40,787 --> 00:56:42,997
Machinery,

789
00:56:43,081 --> 00:56:46,501
The machinery's working, Catherine,

790
00:56:46,584 --> 00:56:51,965
It's on full blast,
All the cylinders are firing,

791
00:56:52,006 --> 00:56:54,342
I'm on fire,

792
00:56:55,510 --> 00:57:00,181
That's why I came out here to cool off,
I haven't felt like this for years,

793
00:57:00,265 --> 00:57:02,016
- You're kidding,
- No,

794
00:57:02,100 --> 00:57:06,813
- I don't believe it,
- I don't believe it either, but it's true,

795
00:57:06,854 --> 00:57:09,649
It started about a week ago,
I woke up,

796
00:57:09,732 --> 00:57:12,652
I came downstairs,
made a cup of coffee,

797
00:57:12,735 --> 00:57:17,198
Before I could pour the milk in, it was like
someone turned the light on in my head,

798
00:57:17,281 --> 00:57:20,660
- Really?
- Not the light, The whole grid, I lit up!

799
00:57:20,701 --> 00:57:22,954
It's like no time has passed
since I was 21,

800
00:57:22,995 --> 00:57:25,623
- You're kidding me,
- No, I'm back,

801
00:57:25,706 --> 00:57:30,086
I'm back, In touch with the source!
The font,

802
00:57:30,169 --> 00:57:34,340
Whatever the source of my creativity was
all those years ago, I'm in contact with it,

803
00:57:34,423 --> 00:57:38,386
I'm sitting on it, It's a geyser,
and I'm shooting up in the air on top of it,

804
00:57:38,469 --> 00:57:40,805
God,

805
00:57:40,846 --> 00:57:45,309
I'm not talking about divine inspiration, It's
not funneling into my head, onto the page,

806
00:57:45,393 --> 00:57:49,188
I'm not saying it won't be a lot of work,
It will be, a tremendous amount of work,

807
00:57:49,271 --> 00:57:53,275
It's not gonna be easy,
But the raw material is there,

808
00:57:53,359 --> 00:57:55,986
I see places for the work to go,
new techniques,

809
00:57:56,028 --> 00:58:01,409
I'm gonna get whole branches
of the profession talking to each other,

810
00:58:01,492 --> 00:58:03,369
I'm sorry,

811
00:58:03,410 --> 00:58:05,788
I'm being rude,

812
00:58:07,957 --> 00:58:10,626
- How's school?
- School's fine,

