00:58:10,709 --> 00:58:12,545
- You're working hard?
- Sure,

814
00:58:12,628 --> 00:58:14,505
- Faculty treating you all right?
- Yes,

815
00:58:14,547 --> 00:58:15,923
- Made any friends?
- Yes,

816
00:58:16,006 --> 00:58:17,091
- You dating?
- Dad,

817
00:58:17,174 --> 00:58:20,052
No details necessary
if you don't want to provide them,

818
00:58:20,094 --> 00:58:23,597
School is fine, OK?
I want to talk about what you're doing,

819
00:58:23,681 --> 00:58:25,933
Great, Let's talk,

820
00:58:26,016 --> 00:58:27,893
- This work...
- Yes,

821
00:58:27,976 --> 00:58:30,604
- It's here?
- Part of it, yes,

822
00:58:30,688 --> 00:58:33,065
- Can I see it?
- It's all at a very early stage,

823
00:58:33,148 --> 00:58:34,858
- I don't care,
- It's not complete,

824
00:58:34,900 --> 00:58:38,487
To be honest, it's all in progress,
I think we're talking years,

825
00:58:38,570 --> 00:58:42,116
Dad, it's OK,
Just let me see anything,

826
00:58:42,199 --> 00:58:44,701
- You really want to?
- Yes,

827
00:58:45,744 --> 00:58:48,830
- You're genuinely interested?
- Dad, of course,

828
00:58:48,914 --> 00:58:51,375
Of course, It is your field,

829
00:58:51,458 --> 00:58:53,210
Yes,

830
00:58:53,252 --> 00:58:55,754
You know how happy that makes me?

831
00:58:55,796 --> 00:58:58,090
Yes,

832
00:58:58,131 --> 00:59:02,594
I think there's enough here to keep me
working the rest of my life, And not just me,

833
00:59:02,636 --> 00:59:08,934
I was starting to imagine I was finished,
Catherine, Really finished,

834
00:59:09,017 --> 00:59:13,230
I was terrified I'd never work again,
Did you know that?

835
00:59:14,231 --> 00:59:18,235
- I wondered,
- I was absolutely bloody terrified,

836
00:59:19,945 --> 00:59:23,657
Then I remembered something,
I remembered you,

