01:04:24,371 --> 01:04:27,875
At least, it looks an awful lot
like the writing in the other books,

917
01:04:27,917 --> 01:04:31,754
Maybe your writing looks exactly like his,
I don't know,

918
01:04:33,631 --> 01:04:35,633
It does look like his,

919
01:04:35,716 --> 01:04:39,303
I mean, it's one of his notebooks,
the exact same kind he used,

920
01:04:39,386 --> 01:04:42,890
I told you,
He gave it to me,

921
01:04:46,393 --> 01:04:48,854
I didn't show this to anyone,

922
01:04:51,064 --> 01:04:56,778
