doing lame research,

943
01:06:02,927 --> 01:06:05,680
bragging about
the conferences they go to,

944
01:06:05,722 --> 01:06:07,682
Wow,

945
01:06:07,765 --> 01:06:13,354
Playing in an awful band and whining
that they're intellectually past it at 26,

